    "tutorialText": [
        "Your goal is to keep the plant healthy as long as possible, harvesting the fruit that grows to reach a high score.",
        "The status bars above the plant represent water, light, fruit growth, and overall health.",
        "The bottom bar is the plant's health. Health will improve over time as long as water, light, and hazards are managed.",
        "The tools on the right bar allow managing water and light levels. Select a tool by tapping it and use it by tapping on the plant. Most of the tools won't do anything right now.",
        "The umbrella and watering can tools (the second row) will decrease and increase the water level, respectively.",
        "Water level will increase or decrease naturally depending on the current weather. Use the tools in the second row to keep the plant at a healthy water level.",
        "If the water level is very high or very low, the plant will lose health. If health reaches zero, the plant will die.",
        "Light works similarly to water. The shade and lamp tools (the third row) will decrease and increase the light level, respectively.",
        "The rate of change of water and light is determined by the current weather.",
        "Weather will change every few seconds. A preview of upcoming weather can be seen in the top right.",
        "As long as the plant is not losing health, it will grow fruit periodically. When the fruit becomes red, it can be harvested.",
        "The basket tool in the first row can be used to harvest fruit when it is grown.",
        "The fertilizer tool to the right of the basket can be repeatedly used to increase the speed of fruit growth.",
        "Your score is shown in the top left. It will regularly increase based on the current health of the plant.",
        "Whenever you harvest a fruit, you receive a bonus 100 points.",
        "Tutorial complete! Click Next to return to the main menu."
    ],

